data.description: Harper Creek School District! This 3-bedroom Ranch has the perfect outdoor space for relaxing or for entertaining. The home sits on almost a full acre and has 2 separate fenced areas in the back yard, deck and inground pool! The home also has a partially finished basement that can be transformed into extra living space or used for extra storage. Also enjoy the breezeway that attaches the garage to the home.
